## Summary
This documentation explains methods to manage invalid or erroneous data in Amplitude Data, including drop filters (query-time exclusion), block filters (prevents data ingestion), blocking specific events/properties, and permanently deleting data, with detailed steps for implementing each approach and their key differences.

